      "data": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>Casting a <em>@Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.xRgU9rrhmGAgG4Rc]{Gentle Repose}</em> spell on a carrion golem causes it to grow stiff. The golem attempts a @Check[type:fortitude|dc:19] save. It's unaffected on a critical success, @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.xYTAsEpcJE1Ccni3]{Slowed 1} for [[/br 1d4 #rounds]]{1d4 rounds} on a success, and on a failure is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.eIcWbB5o3pP6OIMe]{Immobilized} and slowed for [[/br 1d4 #rounds]]{1d4 rounds}.</p>"
